{"tid":754841,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"太酷啦！小米推出「平衡車」改裝套件，裝上「秒變卡丁車」！網友興奮直呼：必買！","createTime":"2018-07-24T17:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T01:48:06.000Z","uid":85180,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"60bcada4ffcbe43d4bec6bfef2ce62aa5e4ec44d","tid":754841,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"太酷啦！小米推出「平衡車」改裝套件，裝上「秒變卡丁車」！網友興奮直呼：必買！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2018/07/24/20180724-033139_U9180_M435424_0769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F20180724-033139_U9180_M435424_0769.jpg&h=a50a8424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賽車迷有福啦！小米一車兩用改裝套件亮相，將你的平衡車秒變卡丁車！（圖／Ninebot Segway TW臉書粉專）<br />\n<br />\n電動滑板、平衡車、電動獨輪車躍升為新一代代步工具，其中小米旗下 Ninebot 所推出的 9 號平衡車也是不少人的選擇。近日，官方微博祭出好消息─將推出改裝套件，讓平衡車秒變夢幻卡丁車，眾人賽車魂燃燒。<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2018/07/24/20180724-033139_U9180_M435425_48a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F20180724-033139_U9180_M435425_48a4.jpg&h=2f3a77f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新型代步、娛樂工具越來越夯，於 2015 年收購賽格威的小米騎行生態鏈公司 Ninebot，陸續推出電動溜冰鞋等新玩意兒，這回竟看上了夢幻「卡丁車」。<br />\n<br />\n據官方微博消息，「9 號平衡車卡丁改裝套件」顧名思義，能讓現有 9 號平衡車（中國版）和 Ninebot Segway miniPro（國際版），變身為卡丁車。<br />\n加上改裝套件，平衡車竟然能變身卡丁車！（圖／Ninebot Segway TW 臉書粉專）<br />\n從官方曝光的照片來看，這款套件為平衡車增加了可調整高度的座椅、煞車系統、前保險桿、方向盤和免充氣前輪，以及具有緩衝保護效果的車殼和強化車體結構強度的鋼材主樑。原先的平衡車則用於後輪，為該卡丁車驅動。<br />\n如此逆天的改裝套件，也使無數網友熱血沸騰，留言表示「必買！」、「逆天了！」、「中國F1 的未來」，不少民眾也紛紛詢問發售日期和價格，然而官方目前並沒有回應。<br />\n<br />\n不過，據外媒 Abacus 報導，該平衡車卡丁改裝套件將於美國時間 7 月 24 日，在洛杉磯進行發表，屆時可能會透露更多詳細資訊。<br />\n<br />\n作為「小孩的大玩具、老頑童的小賽車」，勢必會再掀起一番平衡車、卡丁車熱潮，讓親子間的娛樂擁有更多選擇。<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2018/07/24/20180724-033139_U9180_M435426_3920.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F20180724-033139_U9180_M435426_3920.jpg&h=9b9c16c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efe371d27f1261679dfc0b57c699d377d5156c44","tid":754841,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hess0802.pixnet.net/album/photo/134285275-dao_02.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhess0802.pixnet.net%2Falbum%2Fphoto%2F134285275-dao_02.gif&h=ceab3f7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa28bdc31e76e136e8e52c39dfa820be75ed85ba","tid":754841,"uid":85180,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_lj7vqclVzz1qg6hh1o1_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Ftumblr_lj7vqclVzz1qg6hh1o1_500.jpg&h=4177a6c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e6a051c29afb8eba839d3329075981482de44f2","tid":754841,"uid":12404,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.duniafintech.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Boom-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.duniafintech.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2FBoom-2.png&h=faa5012f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ceda4726e46c1e8266b7e2307b560e604d329f2","tid":754841,"uid":45830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:10:43.000Z","msg":"等睇人炒車"},{"pid":"21784909fb4e1dc8e1e10668843cbb60c08c100d","tid":754841,"uid":127947,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"等睇香港班蝗買落黎<br />\n比差佬告無牌架駛"},{"pid":"e817f45644014fddf4f647768bbcaf312bf01d3a","tid":754841,"uid":80176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T18:43:52.000Z","msg":"老實講個idea幾好<br />\n不過唔知係咪抄啦<img src